The Creative Act: A Way of Being by Rick Rubin Link to heading The Creative Act by Rick Rubin is an inspiring essay that offers valuable insights into the creative process, emphasizing the importance of authenticity, collaboration, and experimentation in unlocking one’s creative potential.

item.title: About
item.description: Hi, My name is Zeeshan Chatur and I am from Dallas, Texas. I am currently a student at Texas A&M University majoring in Management Information Systems. I am passionate about data analytics, machine learning and AI. I am always on the lookout for new things and advancements in these areas. Data is one of the things I love and I am driven by the desire to uncover insights, patterns and trends that can help understand the world better.

item.title: Projects
item.description: One Byte: Pizza Review Analysis Link to heading Welcome to One Byte, a data analysis project that analyzes the data from Dave Portnoy’s One Bite Pizza series. The One Bite Pizza reviews started in 2014 and have really gained popularity since 2016, with a new review being uploaded almost daily since then. As a fan of pizza, I have always been searching for the perfect slice. That’s why I have analyzed over 1300 pizza locations reviewed by Dave Portnoy in his One Bite Pizza series to bring you the ultimate guide to finding the best pizza.
